headline.main: Teed Off: Critics Say Trump Water Rule Helps His Golf Links
headline.print_headline: Teed Off: Critics Say Trump Water Rule Helps His Golf Links

lead_paragraph: President Donald Trump's recent executive order calling for a review of a rule protecting small bodies of water from pollution and development is strongly supported by golf course owners who are wary of being forced into expensive cleanups on their fairways.
